  "title": "Even More Instruments!",
  "description": "Violins, Guitars, Keyboards, and Even More Instruments to add into your Minecraft experience!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/N1s2APm.png\" alt=\"Banner\" width=\"1903\" height=\"507\" /></p><center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><h1 style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Add even more instruments to your Minecraft experience!</h1></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Tired of just goat horns being your way of musical expression? Or maybe you've had enough of your Genshin instruments?</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Look no further than the Even More Instruments mod!</span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #ff0000; --darkreader-inline-color: #ff1a1a;\" data-darkreader-inline-color=\"\"><strong>! This mod requires <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/genshin-instruments/\">Genshin Instruments</a> v4.0 or higher !</strong></span></p></center>\n<!--<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join the Development Livestream!</strong></h1>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YOqkeE_30Ik?wmode=transparent\" width=\"638\" height=\"358\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><hr/>-->\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tDIAfkaUNag\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rnMmBKchqfI\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<br/>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1CVVqa2BHVE\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<br/>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NhZKh6O5eGQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<hr /><center>\n<p><h3><strong>Are you a content creator? Instrument player?</strong></h3></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Reach out to me in <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/private-messages/send?recipient=stavwasplays\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CurseForge PMs</a> to have your video showcased <strong>here</strong>!</span></p>\n</center><hr /><br/>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⚠️ IMPORTANT ⚠️: The Mod Author has Retired the project</strong></h2>\n<p>Watch the video below to learn more:</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TUzdklT4vcs?wmode=transparent\" width=\"638\" height=\"358\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>  \n<h3>This mod adds the following instruments to the game:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Trombone</li>\n<li>Violin (Long and short notes - cycle with Right Alt!)</li>\n<li>Keyboard (and a stand!)</li>\n<li>Guitar</li>\n<li>Saxophone</li>\n<li>Various Asian/Japanese instruments:\n<ul>\n<li>Koto</li>\n<li>Shamisen &amp; Bachi</li>\n<li>Pipa (Regular &amp; Tremolo)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>All 16 note blocks as playable instruments!</li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bCLnB21RSj4\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Looper</h2>\n<p>Loop over your music using the Looper! Add background tracks and juice up your plays, without the need for a second foe to memorize your tracks!</p>\n<h2>Records</h2>\n<p>Record tracks, and share them with friends! Use the<strong> <em>/emirecord</em></strong> command to export &amp; burn records, and enjoy the beauty of coorperation ✨</p>\n<p>Find your exported records under your world's&nbsp;<em>generated</em> directory.</p>\n<h2>Full MIDI Support!</h2>\n<p>As part of the Genshin Instruments mod, all instruments have native MIDI support - just like their counterparts at the parent mod!</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WaCIP4lWEzk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MhHqXmaiCZA\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7PKk7qorFTk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Pre-Burned Records</h2>\n<p>Scattered across your Minecraft worlds, you may find random records - left behind by some unkown entity... 0-0</p>\n<h3>All records and their locations:</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Super Idol - De Xian Rong</strong>: Jungle Temple</li>\n<li><strong>Sad Romance - Ji Pyeongkeyon</strong>: Savanna villages</li>\n<li><strong>Timmy Trumpet &amp; Savage - Freaks</strong>: Bastions</li>\n<li><strong>Interesting Record</strong>: Abandoned Mineshafts</li>\n<li><strong>H&auml;nschen klein - Franz Wiedemann</strong>: Buried Treasure</li>\n</ol>\n\n<br/>\n<details>\n<summary>\"Interesting Record\"? What about it?</summary>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?si=ltxfCMLOt79VN4BM\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</details>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Multiplayer Support!</h2>\n<p>This mod is fully compatible with servers, and is optimized to run at them.</p>\n<p>*Thus, loopers cap at 255 notes - modifiable via the evenmoreinstruments_looperMaxNotes gamerule</p>",
